## ✅ **VALIDATION EXPLAINED**

### **In Middleware**

```javascript
router.post("/invoice", 
    validateRequestBody({
        requiredFields: ["InvNumber", "SellerName", "BuyerName"],
        customValidator: (body) => {
            if (!isValidInvoiceNumber(body.InvNumber)) {
                return {
                    isValid: false,
                    errors: ["Invalid invoice format"]
                };
            }
            return { isValid: true, errors: [] };
        }
    }),
    controller.createInvoice
);
```

