## 🏗️ **BEST PRACTICES**

✅ **Always use `asyncHandler`** to wrap async functions  
✅ **Validate in middleware** before controller receives data  
✅ **Throw custom errors** from services/controllers  
✅ **Use repositories** for all database queries  
✅ **Keep services focused** on business logic  
✅ **Use Prisma ORM** for standard queries, raw SQL for complex ones  
✅ **Never query database directly** from controllers  
✅ **Log important events** for debugging  
✅ **Use environment variables** for sensitive data  
✅ **Return consistent response format** from all endpoints  

